						<summary>

						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Śaka 1413 (1492 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>Registers a gift of the villages Kōramaṅgala, Ariyamaṅgalappaṭṭi and two other villages (name not clear) as <hi rend="italic">sarvamānya</hi> to the god for feeding Brāhmaṇas daily at Śrīraṅga. The donor's name is lost. The details of the date viz. <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1413, Virōdhikṛit, Phālguṇa, śu. 10, Monday,</hi> are irregular. <hi rend="bold">If śu 10 is a mistake for śu 1,</hi> the details regularly correspond to <hi rend="bold">1492 A.D., January 10.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
